 sustaining team.   ·         Advanced/expert fluency in C  ·         Experience working with UNIX/Linux kernels, or other Operating Systems experience  ·         Operational knowledge of Enterprise Linux distributions (Oracle, Red Hat, CentOS, SuSE).  ·         Knowledge of bash, perl, and/or python  ·         Oracle knowledge is not required  ·         At least two years of industry experience working on large software projects.  ·         Experienced in low layer which include CPU architecture   ·         good at SPARC is a big plus                                                                            职位联系方式                                                      公司名称：甲骨文（中国）软件系统有限公司公司地址：海淀区中关村软件园24号楼 传真：82826455公司主页：http://www.oracle.com/') ;
