                          VALUES(currval('"hero_reduce"."user_id_seq"'),'634619621250662.htm','北京','证券分析/金融研究','','“品今•今英会”实习计划品今（北京）资产管理有限公司是品今控股集团旗下全资子公司。品今资管旨在为高净值个人、富有家族及机构投资人提供股权投资基金、金融市场投资基金和家族财富管理等多样化资产管理服务。    品今资管是国内领先的资产管理机构，其网络遍布全国。通过严格的产品筛选体系和风险控制体系，品今资管为高端客户提供全能型资产管理服务，实现其资产的保值增值。品今资管现面向在校本科生、研究生推出2014年实习计划，本实习计划着眼于培养中国下一代投资银行家，打造金融业精英的朋友圈。本实习计划的内容包括：金融市场相关领域知识的系统培训，导师带领下的专题研究等，涉及的实习岗位包括行业研究、基金研究、PE投资研究、产品设计、市场营销等。参与本实习计划的要求：国内211大学或同等水平院校在读本科生、研究生。所学专业为金融财经类或理工类，年龄28周岁以下，性别不限。  有意向参与本实习计划者，请于2014年6月30日前将个人简历（附照片）发送至liuxiaodong@pinjinchina.com，请勿以其它方式投递简历。     Pin Jin (Beijing) Asset Management Co., Ltd. is a wholly-owned subsidiary of Pin Jin Holding Group (HK) Co., Ltd. Our company aims to provide diversified asset management services for high-net-worth individuals, wealthy families and institutional investors. Our services include PE funds and investment funds in financial market, family wealth management and so forth.   Our company, a leading domestic asset management institution, has its network all over the country. We provide clients with comprehensive asset management services by strict product screening system and risk control system, with the goal to achieve the maintenance and appreciation of asset value.   Our company plans to launch “2014 Summer Internship Programme”, targeting undergraduates and graduates. The Programme focuses on cultivating the next generation of investment bankers and forming a friend circle of financial elites in China. The content of the Programme include: systematic training of knowledge in financial market, research guided by mentors and so forth. We provide positions like specialists of industry research, funds, PE investment, product design, marketing and so forth.   Requirements for the Programme:   l  Undergraduates and graduates of Peking University, Tsinghua University, Renmin University of China, University of International Business and Economics, Central University of Finance and Economics, or other colleges and universities of the same level.   l  Students major in finance and economics, science and engineering.   l  Age: under 28 years old.  l  All genders.  If you are interested in the Programme, please send your resume (photo attached) to liuxiaodong@pinjinchina.com before June 30, 2014. This is the only way for us to receive your resume.                                                                             职位联系方式                                                      公司名称：品今(北京)资产管理有限公司公司地址：北京市朝阳区东三环北路23号财富三期49层传真：公司主页：') ;
